        "content": "<p>Quite often I would like to have sledgehammer find a proof using an explicit fact by name and not just based on simp. How could I restrict sledgehammer to not find a proof by simp or auto?</p>",
        "id": 345064445,
        "sender_full_name": "waynee95",
        "timestamp": 1679993257
